rates of CYP450 3A4, such as cyclosporine.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/97000/', '[1] "Product Information. Orladeyo (berotralstat)." BioCryst Pharmaceuticals Inc, Durham, NC.[2] "Product Information. Intelence (etravirine)." Ortho Biotech Inc, Bridgewater, NJ.', 'Nitric Oxide, Doxapram, Elexacaftor, Lumacaftor', 'Hemin, Conestat alfa, Betibeglogene autotemcel, Hyaluronidase, Streptokinase, Human C1-esterase inhibitor, Crizanlizumab, Lanadelumab, Icatibant', 1767369485);
